physical_appearance: This is a photograph of a boat on a water body in Rangoon (Yangon), Burma. In the middle of the photograph, there is a long boat with many rowers, and one man at the front of the boat on the left. At the back of the boat on the right, there is one passenger in a suit and tophat. In the background of the photograph, there are several ships docked. The title is written at the bottom, below the photograph.
title_text: Photograph album of views and portraits in the Punjab, Cashmere, Ceylon, Burma, Penang, Singapore, and Java Up Country Boat, Rangoon
